lass=\"fn\">docComment</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">Elab.TermElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">VersoDocResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Adds a Verso docstring to the specified declaration, which should already be present in the\nenvironment. The docstring is added from a string value, rather than syntax, which means that the\ninteractive features are disabled.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoDocStringFromString","kind":"def","line":296,"name":"Lean.versoDocStringFromString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L296-L304"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoModDocString\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">versoModDocString</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">range</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/DeclarationRange.html#Lean.DeclarationRange\">DeclarationRange</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">doc</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Doc.Parser.document</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">Elab.TermElabM</a> (<a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.VersoModuleDocs.Snippet\">VersoModuleDocs.Snippet</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">Doc.DeferredCheck</a></span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Parses and elaborates a Verso module docstring.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoModDocString","kind":"def","line":285,"name":"Lean.versoModDocString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L285-L292"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoDocString\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">versoDocString</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">binders</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">docComment</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Command.docComment</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">Elab.TermElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">VersoDocResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elaborates a Verso docstring for the specified declaration, which should already be present in the\nenvironment.\n\n`binders` should be the syntax of the parameters to the constant that is being documented, as a null\nnode that contains a sequence of bracketed binders. It is used to allow interactive features such as\ndocument highlights and “find references” to work for documented parameters. If no parameter binders\nare available, pass `Syntax.missing` or an empty null node.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoDocString","kind":"def","line":250,"name":"Lean.versoDocString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L250-L281"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoDocStringOfText\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">versoDocStringOfText</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">binders</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">docComment</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">Elab.TermElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">VersoDocResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Parses a Verso docstring from its text and elaborates it for the specified declaration. Because the\ntext carries no source positions, interactive features are disabled and any messages are reported at\nthe current reference.\n\n`binders` should be the syntax of the parameters to the constant that is being documented, as a null\nnode that contains a sequence of bracketed binders, or an empty null node when none are available.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.versoDocStringOfText","kind":"def","line":217,"name":"Lean.versoDocStringOfText","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L217-L246"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.deferredChecks\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">VersoDocResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">deferredChecks</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">VersoDocResult</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">Doc.DeferredCheck</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks that cannot be carried out during elaboration, typically because they require information\nthat is not yet available.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.deferredChecks","kind":"def","line":186,"name":"Lean.VersoDocResult.deferredChecks","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L186-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.toVersoDocString\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">VersoDocResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">toVersoDocString</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">VersoDocResult</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.VersoDocString\">VersoDocString</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.toVersoDocString","kind":"def","line":181,"name":"Lean.VersoDocResult.toVersoDocString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L181-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">VersoDocResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.VersoDocString\">Lean.VersoDocString</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck</a></span> → <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\">Lean.VersoDocResult</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult.mk","kind":"ctor","line":177,"name":"Lean.VersoDocResult.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L177-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">VersoDocResult</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span id=\"Lean.VersoDocResult.toVersoDocString\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.VersoDocString\">Lean.VersoDocString</a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The result of elaborating a Verso docstring, which consists of the docstring contents paired with a\nset of deferred checks.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.VersoDocResult","kind":"structure","line":177,"name":"Lean.VersoDocResult","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L177-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.reportVersoParseFailure\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">reportVersoParseFailure</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Position.html#Lean.MonadFileMap\">MonadFileMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Exception.html#Lean.MonadError\">MonadError</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.MonadEnv\">MonadEnv</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.MonadOptions\">MonadOptions</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Log.html#Lean.MonadLog\">MonadLog</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/ResolveName.html#Lean.MonadResolveName\">MonadResolveName</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">parseFailure</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reports parse errors from a Verso docstring parse failure.\n\nWhen Verso docstring parsing fails at parse time, a `parseFailure` node is created containing the\nraw text, because emitting an error at that stage could lead to unwanted parser backtracking. This\nfunction reports the actual error messages with proper source positions.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.reportVersoParseFailure","kind":"def","line":117,"name":"Lean.reportVersoParseFailure","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L117-L174"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.parseVersoDocString\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">parseVersoDocString</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Position.html#Lean.MonadFileMap\">MonadFileMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Exception.html#Lean.MonadError\">MonadError</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.MonadEnv\">MonadEnv</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.MonadOptions\">MonadOptions</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Log.html#Lean.MonadLog\">MonadLog</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/ResolveName.html#Lean.MonadResolveName\">MonadResolveName</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">docComment</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">[</a><span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Command.docComment</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Command.moduleDoc</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">]</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Parses a docstring as Verso, returning the syntax if successful.\n\nWhen not successful, parser errors are logged.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.parseVersoDocString","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"Lean.parseVersoDocString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Add.lean#L47-L112"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Add.html#Lean.validateDocComment\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">validateDocComment</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#MonadLiftT\">MonadLiftT</a> <a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Log.html#Lean.MonadLog\">MonadLog</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.AddMessageContext\">AddMessageContext</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.MonadOptions\">MonadOptions</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">docstring</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Command.docComment</span>)</span></span